Rick Bayless: Seven too.

00:00:35.590 --> 00:00:38.550
Olivia Wu: Seventh season in, in Mexico: "One
Plate at a Time". So,so welcome. Why don't

00:00:38.550 --> 00:00:42.210
you start by saying what this book is about
