00:42:07.010 --> 00:42:11.910
of people.
And so, we're at her house â€“ north -- one

00:42:11.910 --> 00:42:15.920
of the northern suburbs of Chicago -- and
we're havin' just this -- starting to have

00:42:15.920 --> 00:42:21.060
all this amazing things.
