00:42:29.430 --> 00:42:35.940
And at one moment during the -- most of the
things â€“ the meals that we would have, things

00:42:35.940 --> 00:42:41.330
would sort of just spin out of control. And
my favorite memory ever -- ever, ever -- of

00:42:41.330 --> 00:42:48.760
having one of these parties at Olivia's house
