00:42:48.760 --> 00:42:50.820
at one point -- like children's camp songs.

00:42:50.820 --> 00:42:51.820
Olivia Wu: Chinese New Year.

00:42:51.820 --> 00:42:55.710
Rick Bayless: And all of a sudden, and all
of a sudden, we're not paying any attention,

00:42:55.710 --> 00:43:01.430
but we haven't finished our food yet.
