00:43:06.480 --> 00:43:10.140
at this thing with great horror.
And I think my mother is never gonna come

00:43:10.140 --> 00:43:15.900
back and visit me and my friends again.
But it was the most glorious moment that I've

00:43:15.900 --> 00:43:19.870
ever had at any party.
And I always think about that -- singing camp

00:43:19.870 --> 00:43:23.820
songs and watching the dog eat my food off
of my plate. [laughter]

00:43:23.820 --> 00:43:32.240
Olivia Wu: Okay, Barney. Kudos to Barney.
